dct_title_s: Islas Santanilla o de El Cisne, Honduras, C.A.
dct_description_sm: Honduras. Instituto Geografico Nacional. Alternate title: Islas Santanilla o de El Cisne. Universal transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 2 m. contour interval and spot heights. Depths shown by soundings in meters. Sheet 1: Isla Grande. Sheet 2: Isla peque~na. 1971
